707358f.title: Brooklyn: 5th St. (S.) - 4th St. S.
707358f.text:
Williamsbrug Bridge Plaza. between South 5th Street (left)
and South 4th Street (right), showing in the Plaza a statue of
George Washington. Also shown at the N.W. corner of the Plara is
the Williamsbrug Trust Co. Building. The South 3rd Street
Presbyterian Church spire is seen in the center right of the view.
About 1914
Urbrock Collection
MAY BE REPEOIUOED
